ygData.msgSnippet: Kill stuff in Eastern Wastes: Ulthorks, Walrus, maybe some other stuff. Save 4 Ulthork tusks and hand them to the right otter and he will give you a nice prize
ygData.messageBody:
Kill stuff in Eastern Wastes: Ulthorks, Walrus, maybe some other stuff.
Save 4 Ulthork tusks and hand them to the right otter and he will give you a
nice prize (random good gem: diamond, blue diamond, sapphire, jacinth) - be
careful, the way the npc's are positioned, it is a common mistake to hand
your 4 tusks to the wrong otter even though you are standing right in front
of and talking to the correct one.

Sylly

-----Original Message-----
From: Nygaard, Jeff [mailto:jeff.nygaard@...]
Sent: Friday, August 24, 2001 11:19 AM
To: eqbards@yahoogroups.com
Subject: RE: [eqbards] eqbards@yahoogroups.com


Yes, Cobalt Scars otters are on a stand alone faction. Everyone starts out
indifferent and moves from there. I don't know of anyway to improve faction
with them.
